data.description: Price improvement with a $15,000 price reduction. Now priced at $585,000 make this home for the Holidays and Ring in the new year ! Don't wait, drive by this home today. Located in one of Madera's most desirable and fastest selling communities (Riverstone). Beautifully Maintained and Upgraded ! Spacious and Open, you will not be disappointed. 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, plus an Office. Upgraded extra large refrigerator, window shades, tile floors, granite counter tops, subway tile backsplash, custom backyard, has already been completed for you. In addition this home has expanded / paid off solar (with outlet to charge your car) ! The large primary bedroom has a walk in closet, soaking tub, dual vanities, and separate shower. You will love the high ceilings and open concept that allows the flow through out the home. Indoor laundry, finished garage, and tankless water heater. Don't hesitate to see this home today and make an appointment. You will have access to all the amenities of the Clubhouse, gym, pool, schools, and new developing restaurants near by. Easy access to Freeway 41, so close to Fresno and the Riverpark shopping area.
